    {
      "locale": "frFR",
      "text": "« Puisque vous dites être collègues, pourquoi ne pas travailler ensemble ? »",
      "modification_date": "2026-04-27T09:11:52.3434288Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-04-27T09:11:52.3434290Z",
      "original_text": "\"If you call each other colleagues, why do you not work together?\"",
      "traits": [
