          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-04-27T09:11:52.3434295Z",
          "locale_text": "« Puisque vous dites être collègues, pourquoi ne pas travailler ensemble ? »"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“既然你们互称同僚，为什么不一起合作？”",
      "modification_date": "2026-04-28T14:25:44.7000824Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-04-28T14:25:44.7000826Z",
      "original_text": "\"If you call each other colleagues, why do you not work together?\"",
